          <li><a href="#applications-whpx" class="text-[#1B3A5C] hover:text-[#E8A317]">WHPX-407 Applications</a></li>
          <li><a href="#specifications-whpx" class="text-[#1B3A5C] hover:text-[#E8A317]">WHPX-407 Specifications</a></li>
          <li><a href="#wspx-207" class="text-[#1B3A5C] hover:text-[#E8A317]">Alfa Laval WSPX 207</a></li>
