  <!-- Main Content -->
  <section class="bg-[#F5F5F0] pb-16">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-4xl">

      <div class="bg-navy/5 border-l-4 border-gold rounded-r-lg p-4 mb-6">
        <p class="text-sm text-text-light leading-relaxed italic">The Alfa Laval MOPX 207 centrifuge is a self-cleaning three-phase disc stack centrifuge rated at 33–40 GPM (20–26 GPM on diesel). Dolphin Centrifuge supplies the MOPX 207 as the DMPX-028 complete centrifuge module — a fully integrated system processing fuel oil, lube oil, and waste oil continuously at 7,000–7,800 Gs. Based in Warren, Michigan, Dolphin Centrifuge has over 40 years of experience in MOPX-series centrifuge systems and applications.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- MOPX 207 Operation -->
      <div id="operation" class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-gray-100 shadow-sm p-6 md:p-8 mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#1B3A5C] mb-4">Alfa Laval MOPX 207 — Operation</h2>
        <p class="text-[#2D2D2D] leading-relaxed mb-4">
          The <a href="https://www.alfalaval.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-[#E8A317] hover:underline">Alfa Laval</a> MOPX 207 Centrifuge is a self-cleaning, <a href="/disc-stack-centrifuge/" class="text-[#E8A317] hover:underline">disc-stack centrifuge</a> ideal for the continuous, three-phase separation of fuels and mineral oils.
        </p>
        <p class="text-[#2D2D2D] leading-relaxed mb-4">
          With a <strong>7.5 HP Motor</strong>, the MOPX 207 centrifuge has a bowl RPM of <strong>6,325</strong> and can process <strong>32 GPM of Distillate</strong>.
        </p>
        <p class="text-[#2D2D2D] leading-relaxed mb-4">
          The Alfa Laval MOPX-207 is a versatile, 'self-cleaning' centrifuge that is small enough to be manually serviced without the need for lifting devices (cranes, hoists, etc.)
        </p>
        <p class="text-[#2D2D2D] leading-relaxed mb-6">
          However, it can process over 30 Gallons per Minute of condensate.
        </p>

        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 items-center">
          <figure class="flex-shrink-0">
            <img
              src="/images/alfa-laval-mopx-207-centrifuge/Alfa-Laval-MOPX207-Used-Oil-Centrifuge-600.jpg"
